an be a few minutes,\nas opposed to Sweet-Parker's equivalent value of < a day. The new theoretical\nreconnection rate is compared to the MRX device experimental data by [Yamada et\nal., Phys. Plasmas, 13, 052119 (2006), Ji et al. GRL, 35, 13106 (2008)] and a\ngood agreement is obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Aug 2008 16:24:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Aug 2008 10:36:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 6 Aug 2008 11:44:37 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 26 Sep 2008 09:16:21 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 31 Oct 2008 11:07:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-12-23"}
